\begin_layout Abstract
This protocol is an attempt to fabricate gold disks from solution.
 The target is a hexagon with side length 50 to 100 microns and diameter
 at least 20 nm.
 This protocol has been adapted from previous attempts to fabricate these
 disks.
 All observations have been included for future use.
