\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Standard
A modification to the previous protocol was the addition of three filtration
 steps.
 After the preparation of the gold chloride solution in milli-Q distilled
 water, a single filtration was performed.
 The pH meter was then recalibrated, and 80 
\begin_inset Formula $\mu l$
\end_inset

